@page
@model LicenseModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "License Terms";
}

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">ePegboard License Terms</h1>
        <p>Last updated: May 2026 - interim, pending paid legal review</p>

        <p><strong>By using ePegboard (either the web app at play.epegboard.com or the desktop application), you agree to the following terms.</strong></p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Web app (play.epegboard.com)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Free to use:</strong> the web app is free to use, with full functionality and no payment or card details required.</li>
            <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> the club-night workflow is free, and there will always be a free plan. We will give at least 60 days' notice before any pricing change takes effect.</li>
            <li><strong>Data export:</strong> your club can export its data (member list, session history, etc.) at any time.</li>
            <li><strong>Data deletion:</strong> you may request deletion of your club's data at any time via <a href="mailto:admin@epegboard.com">admin@epegboard.com</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>Availability:</strong> we aim for high uptime but the web app is not guaranteed to be available 24/7. We will notify users ahead of planned maintenance where possible.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Desktop app (Windows)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>License type:</strong> per-club license, valid for use on a single computer at a time. Non-transferable; may not be reassigned to another club without written permission.</li>
            <li><strong>Trial period:</strong> 60-day free trial with full, unrestricted functionality. No payment or registration required to activate the trial.</li>
            <li><strong>License term and expiry:</strong> a full license entitles the club to use the software for 12 months from the date of activation. After expiry, the software becomes inaccessible until a renewal key is entered. Prior to expiry, clubs can export all data for backup or migration purposes.</li>
            <li><strong>Updates and support:</strong> your license includes all software updates and email support for the duration of the license period.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Both versions - usage restrictions</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>The software may not be redistributed, resold, sublicensed, reverse-engineered, or decompiled.</li>
            <li>It may not be used for commercial resale, software-as-a-service hosting, or any purpose outside your club's own use.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Ownership</h3>
        <p>
            ePegboard is developed and owned by <strong>MBS Software Limited</strong>. All intellectual property rights remain with the developer.
        </p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Contact</h3>
        <p>
            For licence enquiries or to renew your desktop licence, please email:<br />
            📧 <a href="mailto:sales@epegboard.com">sales@epegboard.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
